Package org.anchoranalysis.feature.session.cache.horizontal

Class HorizontalCalculationCache<T extends FeatureInput>

Object
HorizontalCalculationCache<T>
Type Parameters:
T - feature-input type
All Implemented Interfaces:
FeatureSessionCache<T>
public class HorizontalCalculationCache<T extends FeatureInput>
extends Object
implements FeatureSessionCache<T>
Caches CachedCalculations that occur repeatedly across many features, and store similar child caches.

The caches are reset every time invalidate() is called.

Author:
Owen Feehan
